  <Section class=unnumbered>
    <Title/Creating a Ball/  

    <P>
      Click the left mouse button to create a ball at the 
      current mouse pointer position.
    </P>

  </Section>

  <Section class=unnumbered>
    <Title/Deleting a Ball/  

    <P>
     Click the right mouse button to delete the ball that has been
     created last.
    </P>

  </Section>


